quran[5{c,v,t}:
5,46,phir hum ne un payghambaroon ke baad maryam ke betay eesa ko bheja Touraat mein se jo kuch is ke samnay mojood tha woh is ki tasdeeq karne wala tha aur hum ne is ko injeel ataa ki jis mein rahnumai aur roshni thi aur woh bhi Touraat mein se jo kuch uss waqt mojood tha uss ki tasdeeq karne wali thi aur khuda taras logon ke liye sara sar hadaayat aur nasiyaat thi
5,47,hamara hukum tha ke ahal injeel is qanoon ke mutabiq faisla karen jo Allah ne is mein nazil kya hai aur jo log Allah ke nazil kardah qanoon ke mutabiq faisla nah karen wohi fasik hain
5,48,"phir ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! hum ne tumhari taraf yeh kitaab bhaije jo haq le kar aayi hai aur al-kitab mein se jo kuch is ke agay mojood hai uss ki tasdeeq karne wali aur is ki Muhafiz o nigehbaan hai lehaza tum khuda ke nazil kardah qanoon ke mutabiq logon ke mamlaat ka faisla karo aur jo haq tumahray paas aaya hai uss se mun mourr kar un ki khwahisaat ki pairwi nah karo hum ne tum mein se har aik ke liye aik Shariat aur aik raah amal muqarrar ki agarchay tumhara khuda chahta to tum sab ko aik ummat bhi bana sakta tha, lekin uss ne yeh iss liye kya ke jo kuch uss ne tum logon ko diya hai is mein tumhari azmaish kere lehaza bhulaiyon mein aik dosray se Sabqat le jaane ki koshish karo aakhir-kaar tum sab ko khuda ki taraf palat kar jana hai, phir woh tumhe asal haqeeqat bta day ga jis mein tum ikhtilaaf karte rahay ho"
5,49,"pas ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! tum Allah ke nazil kardah qanoon ke mutabiq inn logon ke mamlaat ka faisla karo aur un ki khwahisaat ki pairwi nah karo hooshiyar raho ke yeh log tum ko fitnah mein daal kar uss hadaayat se zarra barabar munharif nah karne payen jo khuda ne tumhari taraf nazil ki hai phir agar yeh is se mun morhin to jaan lau ke Allah ne inn ke baaz gunaaho ki Padaash mein un ko mbtlaye museebat karne ka iradah hi kar liya hai, aur yeh haqeeqat hai ke inn logon mein se aksar fasik hain"
5,50,( agar yeh khuda ke qanoon se mun morty hain ) to kya phir jahliat ka faisla chahtay hain? halaank jo log Allah par yaqeen rakhtay hain un ke nazdeek Allah se behtar faisla karne wala koi nahi hai
